PRESS DIGEST - RUSSIA - DECEMBER 16 . SEVODNYA - The communists , dominating Russia ' s parliament , have ensured the approval of the 1997 draft budget in first reading but wanted Anatoly Chubais to be sacked in exchange for their support . - Salman Raduyev , known for his hostage - taking raid into Dagestan last January , again seized 22 Russian policemen . - Aslan Maskhadov is ahead of other candidates in the presidential election race , according to a Chechen newspapers survey . NEZAVISIMAYA GAZETA - A behind - the - scene meeting between Russia ' s premier Viktor Chernomyrdin and the left opposition majority of parliament has decided the fate of the vote on the 1997 budget . - Russia ' s armed forces and the whole defence system of the country are in a crisis , says Defence Minister Igor Rodionov . - - Tatyana Ustinova , Moscow Newsroom , + 7095 941 8520 . 
